<p>index_row.design :</p>
<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;box</span> <span class="na">style=</span><span class="s">"#item"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
